1 \leq k \leq n 
\binom{n+k-1}{n-1} = \sum_{i=1}^{k} \binom{k-1}{i-1} \binom{n}{i} 
\sum_{i=1}^k \binom{k-1}{i-1} \binom{n}{n-i}.
